493
00:33:49.571 --> 00:33:53.242
Hmm. Well. I don't know
what he did to you...

494
00:33:54.159 --> 00:33:55.369
[softly] Make it two.

495
00:33:55.452 --> 00:33:58.080
- [clicks tongue] But. in my experience...
- Mm-hmm.

496
00:33:58.163 --> 00:34:00.207
